{"questionId":"24905144","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>In the first month of a reforestation program, the town of Neerim plants <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>85</mn></math> trees.&nbsp;Each subsequent month the number of trees planted will increase by an additional&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>30</mn></math> trees.</p>\n<p>The number of trees to be planted in each of the first three months are shown in the following table.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"__IMG__/b97591756206fbc158df9fc1f2db4d2162c262eb.png\"></p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Find the number of trees to be planted in the <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>15</mn><mtext>th</mtext></math> month.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p>use of the <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi>n</mi><mtext>th</mtext></msup></math> term of an arithmetic sequence formula&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>u</mi><mn>15</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>85</mn><mo>+</mo><mfenced><mrow><mn>15</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>×</mo><mn>30</mn></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>(A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>505</mn></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>[3 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"24905144","referenceCode":"22N.1.SL.TZ0.2a","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Find the number of trees to be planted in the 15th month.","paper":"1","level":"SL","questionNumber":"a","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 3]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 1—Number and algebra","Topic 1—Number and algebra","SL 1.2—Arithmetic sequences and series"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}